com.ansca.corona

Interface CoronaActivity.OnNewIntentResultHandler

  • Enclosing class:
    CoronaActivity

    public static interface CoronaActivity.OnNewIntentResultHandler
    Handler that is invoked by the CoronaActivity when it receives a new Intent from outside the application.

    This handler is assigned to the CoronaActivity via its registerNewIntentResultHandler() method.

    Added in daily build 2016.2869.

    See Also:
    CoronaActivity
